Długi Kąt  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Biała Piska, within Pisz County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  south of Biała Piska,  south-east of Pisz, and  east of the regional capital Olsztyn.
